<div>
  <h1>BlocitOFF</h1>
  <p>BlocitOFF is a To Do list so you can get shit done</p>
  <p>
    <% if current_user %>
        Hello <%= current_user.email %>! <%= link_to "Sign out", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete %>
    <% else %>
    <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> or
    <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> today!
    <% end %>
  </p>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Get shit done</h2>
    <p>BlocitOFF lets you add stuff you need to do.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Only do what is important!</h2>
    <p>BlocitOFF lets you work through the list.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>If you do not get to an item it must not be important</h2>
    <p>BlocitOFF gets rid of items you did not complete after 7 days</p>
  </div>
</div>